column10: Successfully initiated and developed a project from scratch, leading a diverse team of professionals in graphic design, development, and marketing. Employed Vue.js 3 and JavaScript to build dynamic, user-friendly web applications. Demonstrated strong skills in community management by growing the project's audience to over 5,000 members. Effectively handled multiple product developments within the project scope, showcasing abilities in project management and innovative solution development.
column12: In general, I did not allocate a salary for myself and everything went into the project
